import React from 'react' import {useSelector} from "react-redux" function SinglePage() { const image = "https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w1280" const selector = useSelector(state=>state.singleReducer) console.log(selector) return (
{ selector.map((a,b)=>(

{a.original_title}

Language: {a.original_language}
Popularity: {a.popularity}
Release date {a.release_date}
)) }
) } export default SinglePage
